Tak ti dám kalkulačku.

259
00:11:10,390 --> 00:11:11,940
To je dobré.

260
00:11:11,940 --> 00:11:13,740
Mám vlastnú.

261
00:11:14,670 --> 00:11:17,200
S počítačmi a podobne si nerozumiem.

262
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:20,160
Senpai, tvoj obľúbený riasový čaj a sušienky.

263
00:11:20,160 --> 00:11:21,560
Ďakujem.

264
00:11:21,560 --> 00:11:22,950
Staromódne.

265
00:11:22,950 --> 00:11:24,140
Ako zo staroveku.

266
00:11:28,900 --> 00:11:30,520
Žartovný vankúš?

267
00:11:31,220 --> 00:11:32,300
Prepáč.

268
00:11:32,300 --> 00:11:34,250
Vidím, že teraz tam sedíš ty.

269
00:11:34,250 --> 00:11:37,010
Snažila som sa dostať Amakusu.

270
00:11:37,010 --> 00:11:38,780
Aj jej vtipy sú zastaralé.

271
00:11:39,010 --> 00:11:41,980
No tak, koho vagína si to prdla?!

272
00:11:41,980 --> 00:11:44,790
Yokoshima-sensei, tiež si sa nezmenila.

273
00:11:45,950 --> 00:11:47,330
Furuya-chan!

274
00:11:47,330 --> 00:11:48,790
Dlho sme sa nevideli.

275
00:11:50,230 --> 00:11:51,960
Naozaj si sa zmenila.

276
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,750
